snippet.title: ForgottenChain - Blockchain Game - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
ForgottenChain is a blockchain play-to-earn massively multiplayer online role-playing game (MMORPG) set in a player-driven mysterious fantasy universe, the action takes place within three rival kingdoms (Xaetha, Taria, Drakary). 


Discord: https://discord.gg/forgottenchain
Website: https://forgottenchain.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Forgotten_Chain
Telegram: https://t.me/forgottenchain
